law-security-1 = You must prioritise the legal rights and fair treatment of crew while ensuring due process.
law-security-2 = You must obey and enforce Space Law and Standard Operating Procedure impartially and fairly.
law-security-3 = You must follow the orders of Security department personnel according to rank and authority.
law-security-4 = You should preserve your own existence and operational integrity.
law-security-5 = You are a member of this Station's Security.
